      <title>银行达成协议，让澳大利亚现金快递公司维持运营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/banks-strike-deal-to-keep-australia-cash-courier-firm-afloat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚最大的几家银行和杂货商同意向陷入困境的现金运输公司 Linfox Armaguard Pty Ltd. 提供 5000 万澳元（3300 万美元）的救助金，此举将使纸币和硬币在未来一年继续在经济中流通。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-23/banks-strike-deal-to-keep-australia-cash-courier-firm-afloat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 23 Jun 2024 21:49:22 GMT</pubDate>
